Package: breadbin
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         libgtk-4-1, libadwaita-1-0
Description: Commodore 64 game and demo kiosk with cover art
 Breadbin is a GTK4/libadwaita frontend that presents your Commodore 64
 game library as a kiosk with cover art organised by genre.  It also
 includes a demoscene browser (grouped by demoparty) and a SID music
 player, all styled with an authentic C64 colour palette.
 .
 Requires VICE (x64sc) to launch games/demos, and optionally C64 Forever
 for ROM support.
